\"/de/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/HTMLCollection\"><code>HTMLCollection</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/MutationObserver\"><code>MutationObserver</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/NamedNodeMap\"><code>NamedNodeMap</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/NodeIterator\"><code>NodeIterator</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/NodeList\"><code>NodeList</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ProcessingInstruction\"><code>ProcessingInstruction</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Range\"><code>Range</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/StaticRange\"><code>StaticRange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Text\"><code>Text</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextDecoder\"><code>TextDecoder</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextEncoder\"><code>TextEncoder</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TimeRanges\"><code>TimeRanges</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TreeWalker\"><code>TreeWalker</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XMLDocument\"><code>XMLDocument</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p>Die&nbsp;<code><strong>add()</strong></code> Methode des&nbsp;<a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/DOMTokenList\"><code>DOMTokenList</code></a> Interfaces, fügt ein&nbsp;<em>token</em> der Liste an.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">tokenList.add(token1[, token2[, ...]]);</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parameter","title":"Parameter","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"token\">token</dt>\n <dd>Ein <a href=\"/de/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String\"><code>DOMString</code></a> ,welches&nbsp;das&nbsp;<em>token</em>&nbsp;repräsentiert, welches an die Liste angefügt werden soll.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"rückgabewert","title":"Rückgabewert","isH3":true,"content":"<p><code>undefined</code></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"beispiele","title":"Beispiele","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Im folgenden Beispiel erhalten wir die Liste der Klassen&nbsp;eines&nbsp;<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/span\"><code>&lt;span&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> Elementes als&nbsp;<code>DOMTokenList</code>&nbsp; , mit Hilfe von&nbsp;<a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Element/classList\"><code>Element.classList</code></a>. Wir fügen der Liste dann ein neues&nbsp;<em>token</em>&nbsp;an und schreiben die Liste als inhalt in das&nbsp;<code>&lt;span&gt;.</code></p>\n\n<p>Das HTML:</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>span</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>a b c<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span></code></pre></div>\n\n<p>Nun das JavaScript:</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> span <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">querySelector</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"span\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> classes <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> span<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>classList<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nclasses<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">add</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"d\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nspan<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>textContent <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> classes<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<p>Die Ausgabe:</p>\n\n<p><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"Beispiele\" id=\"frame_examples\" width=\"100%\" height=\"60\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/de/docs/Web/API/DOMTokenList/add/_sample_.examples.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></p>\n\n<p>Man kann auch mehrere&nbsp;<em>tokens</em>&nbsp;auf einmal hinzufügen:</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>span<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>classList<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">add</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"d\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"e\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"f\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"spezifikationen","title":"Spezifikationen","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Spezifikation</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Kommentar</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#dom-domtokenlist-add\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">DOM<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von 'add()' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Lebender Standard</span></td>\n   <td>Initial definition</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browser Kompatibilität","id":"browser_kompatibilität","isH3":false,"query":"api.DOMTokenList.add","dataURL":"/de/docs/Web/API/DOMTokenList/add/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\">\n\n<p></p><p></p>\n</div>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Syntax","id":"syntax"},{"text":"Beispiele","id":"beispiele"},{"text":"Spezifikationen","id":"spezifikationen"},{"text":"Browser Kompatibilität","id":"browser_kompatibilität"}],"summary":"Die add() Methode des DOMTokenList Interfaces, fügt ein token der Liste an.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"DOMTokenList.add()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"DOMTokenList.add()","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"DOMTokenList.add()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"DOMTokenList.add()","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"de/web/api/domtokenlist/add","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/de/web/api/domtokenlist/add/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/de/docs/Web","title":"Webtechnologien für Entwickler"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API Referenz"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API/DOMTokenList","title":"DOMTokenList"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API/DOMTokenList/add","title":"DOMTokenList.add()"}],"pageTitle":"DOMTokenList.add() - Web API Referenz | MDN","noIndexing":false}}